{"type":"answer","id":222771,"parentType":"question","parentId":22299,"uid":36980,"contents":"南京彭宇案里法官的坐相。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YOZR5kp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YOZR5kp.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YOZR5kp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1Sq7lXN.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1Sq7lXN.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1Sq7lXN.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n我单纯以人类的身份，对犹太猪发明的共产主义对人性造成扭曲的程度之大，对社会撕裂的程度之深，感到震撼。<br>\n<br>\n人们说这个案子令共产中国的道德倒退了五十年，但共产中国本无道德，没有的东西怎么能倒退呢？这个案子只是把共产社会无道德这一点给复述了一遍而已。","date":"2020-03-29","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}